# Local/Private Instructions Template

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` in the same folder and fill in real values.

## Azure Defaults

- **Subscription Name**: <your-subscription-name>
- **Subscription ID**: <your-subscription-id>
- **Tenant ID**: <your-tenant-id>
- **Resource Group**: <your-resource-group>
- **Location**: <your-location>
- **Static Web App Name**: <your-swa-name>
- **Entra App Registration Name**: <your-app-reg-name>
- **Application (Client) ID**: <your-client-id>

## Constraints

- Do not prompt for subscription selection when running Azure commands
- Do not create new resource groups unless explicitly requested
- Never commit secrets — use GitHub Secrets / Key Vault / environment variables
